title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Boudreau/Fletcher/Micheletti/Russo/Myers
description: #92Noon is back in the Xcel Energy Center penalty box! Wild.com's Dan Myers is the co-host for the first hour when Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau stops by! Wild GM Chuck Fletcher also makes an appearance! Also, BOTH Pat and Joe Micheletti join #92Noon to talk everything from growing up in Hibbing to broadcasting. The Athletic's Michael Russo is also a guest!
